    h2.col-xs-12.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1 Documents

    p.col-xs-12.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1.text-justify Please upload following documents:
    ul.col-xs-11.col-sm-9.col-xs-offset-1.col-sm-offset-2.text-justify(ng-if='sponsor==="skype"')
      li Curriculum Vitae
      li full results of your studies at the last educational institution you attended (i.e. your academic record)
      li describe the topic you plan to cover in your Master’s thesis, or if you have not decided this, describe in general the field you are interested in (up to 1000 characters)
      li essay on the topic “What I will be doing in five years’ time thanks to the Skype foreign studies scholarship” (4500-7000 characters)

    ul.col-xs-11.col-sm-9.col-xs-offset-1.col-sm-offset-2.text-justify(ng-if='sponsor==="lhv"')
      li Motivation letter
      li Curriculum Vitae
      li Academic results of entire study period from the last educational institution attended (academic record)
      li Topic and short description of the bachelor’s thesis (up to 1000 characters)

    ul.col-xs-11.col-sm-9.col-xs-offset-1.col-sm-offset-2.text-justify
      li(ng-repeat='(id, f) in application.file')
        a.file(href='', ng-click='doFileDelete("file", id)', title='Delete file...') {{ f.value }}

    .form-group.col-xs-12.col-sm-5.col-sm-offset-1
      input.form-control(ng-if='!application.file.progress', id='file', type='file', onchange='angular.element(this).scope().doFileUpload(this)')
      .col-xs-12(ng-if='application.file.progress') {{ application.file.progress }}% uploaded. Please wait...

    .spacer.col-xs-12

    a.col-xs-10.col-sm-3.col-xs-offset-1.text-left(href='', ng-click='doCancel()', style='color:red') Cancel application
    a.col-xs-10.col-sm-6.col-xs-offset-1.text-right(ng-show='!sending', href='', ng-click='fakeSave()', style='color:green') Your application is saved and sent to us automatically
    a.col-xs-10.col-sm-6.col-xs-offset-1.text-right(ng-show='sending', href='', ng-click='fakeSave()', style='color:green') Ohh! You didn't believe us.
